DTSTAMP:20260410T010853Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260419T150000
SUMMARY:Art in Action: Woven Fairy House Wall Hangings
DESCRIPTION:Pence Family Art Workshops\nOur fairy houses are back – with
  a twist! Learn how to make a simple loom with sticks and twine\, and weav
 e flowers\, leaves\, and other natural materials to create your very own w
 all hanging. Decorate your woven art piece with moss\, fabric butterflies\
 , beads\, and more to create the perfect fairy hideaway.\n\nArt in Action:
  Woven Fairy House Wall Hangings\nSunday\, April 19\, 1-3 PM\n$5 Members\,
  $10 Non-Members (per person\, all materials included)\n\n**How it works:*
 *\nArt in Action engages kids in art projects that are fun\, creative\, an
 d collaborative with their family members. This is a drop-in program for a
 ges 5-12. No registration in advance is required\, but space and supplies 
 are limited to the first 25 participants and are available on a first come
 \, first served basis.\n\nWhen you arrive\, pay with cash or card at the f
 ront desk. A parent or adult caregiver is required to stay\, but only has 
 to pay for the project for themselves if they are also doing art. Stay as 
 long or as short as you like over the two hour period.\n\nBecome a Member 
 starting at $70/year and save! If you join the Pence Gallery when you atte
 nd this workshop\, you can enjoy Member pricing for Art in Action\, plus r
 eceive a $5 gift certificate to our gift shop as a thank you. Membership s
 upports art for all ages and makes creative moments like this possible—j
 ump in and be part of it.\n\nWe have a different Art in Action family work
 shop every month! Learn more at [https://pencegallery.org/art-in-action/](
 https://pencegallery.org/art-in-action/).\n\nThis unique monthly program i
 s generously sponsored and made possible by Mary Stephens DeWall and Les D
 eWall.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/art-in-action/events/313772338/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260313T235714Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T235714Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
